  "response": "The cost of a 60-minute massage in Houston, TX, can vary widely depending on several factors, including the type of massage, the location, the experience level of the therapist, and the establishment where the service is offered. Here are some general price ranges:\n\n- **Spa or High-End Establishment**: $100 - $150+\n- **Mid-Range Spa or Massage Studio**: $70 - $120\n- **Franchise Massage Chains (e.g., Massage Envy)**: $60 - $100\n- **Independent Massage Therapists**: $50 - $90\n\nKeep in mind that prices can also fluctuate based on demand, time of day, and whether you're a new or returning client. Some places may offer discounts, packages, or memberships that can reduce the cost per session.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date pricing, it\u2019s best to check directly with the massage provider or look at their website for specific rates.",
